snippet.title: Kill The Climbers Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to Steam, a new retro gaming experience called Kill The Climbers!

A mountain and its resident yeti are fed up with mountain climbers clambering around, leaving their garbage and frozen corpses strewn everywhere and prancing around on the peak. How can you help them deal with their climber problem?

Your answer? Kill them with everything you've got!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2257560/Kill_The_Climbers/
